\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\iiint_{E}f(x,y,z)dxdydz=\int_{a}^{b}dx\int_{y_{1}(x)}^{y_{2}(x)}dy\int_{z_{1}(x,y)}^{z_{2}(x,y)}f(x,y,z)dz
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
Можно фиксировать 
\begin_inset Formula $x,y,z$
\end_inset

 в другом порядке.
